{"tid":809831,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[小丑台]以捉齊151小精靈為目標!由最初的Gameboy紅版出發!","createTime":"2018-09-07T13:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T12:06:05.000Z","uid":207470,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c72c086e75ed3570d2f6c1a07a24370c27f91a57","tid":809831,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"大家好, 我係小丑P<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相信大家細細個都喺GameBoy玩過Pokemon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係捉到齊151隻Pokemon嘅人又無好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己就一直都想完成呢個願望,<br />\n同埋周不時都見到講Pokemon嘅Post,搞到我都心癢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上自己一D理由,覺得喺時間實現呢個目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又覺得自己一個玩其實無乜癮, 所以就決定搞個直播同大家一齊玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RjpzUaRXRqk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRjpzUaRXRqk&d=BMbJY0WgbVGfko1TIkX5hy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f8530697\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RjpzUaRXRqk</a><br />\n<br />\n對於Pokemon有興趣嘅朋友仔, 可以留意吓我嘅直播 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我將會喺下星期五 (9月14日) 進行試播, <br />\n及後由9月21日逢星期五起 2030-2230進行直播,<br />\n以捉齊151隻小精靈為目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e865a7eccde34bc3193e7736ed92629199c228e","tid":809831,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/010253_ef80d84441c266ea68258390e9afff36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F010253_e